AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: PlannedCostAmount
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The estimated cost of run-dependent resources and materials planned for consumption
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343822

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: PlannedCostMarkup
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The estimated cost of quantity independent charges
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343823

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: RealizedCostAmount
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The actual cost of run-dependent resource and materials consumption
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343824

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: RealizedCostAdjustment
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The actual cost of quantity independent charges
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343825

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: CostOfPlannedConsumption
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The estimated cost of the resources and materials planned for consumption
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343826
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression:
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[CostOfPlannedConsumption] AS IIF ( IsEmpty([Measures].[PlannedCostAmount]) OR IsEmpty([Measures].[PlannedCostMarkup]) ,NULL ,Round ( [Measures].[PlannedCostAmount] + [Measures].[PlannedCostMarkup] ,2 ) )
,VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: CostOfActualConsumption
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The actual cost of the resources and materials that were consumed
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343827
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression:
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[CostOfActualConsumption] AS IIF ( IsEmpty([Measures].[RealizedCostAmount]) OR IsEmpty([Measures].[RealizedCostAdjustment]) ,NULL ,Round ( [Measures].[RealizedCostAmount] + [Measures].[RealizedCostAdjustment] ,2 ) )
,VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: ActualVsPlannedConsumption
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The percentage of difference between the estimated cost of resource and material consumption and the actual cost. The calculation is based on the estimated cost.
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343816
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression:
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[ActualVsPlannedConsumption] AS IIF ( IsEmpty ( ( [Measures].[CostOfActualConsumption] ,[CostCalculation].[ProductionStatus].&[7] ) ) OR IsEmpty ( ( [Measures].[CostOfPlannedConsumption] ,[CostCalculation].[ProductionStatus].&[7] ) ) OR ( [Measures].[CostOfPlannedConsumption] ,[CostCalculation].[ProductionStatus].&[7] ) = 0 ,NULL ,Round ( ( [Measures].[CostOfActualConsumption] ,[CostCalculation].[ProductionStatus].&[7] ) / ( [Measures].[CostOfPlannedConsumption] ,[CostCalculation].[ProductionStatus].&[7] ) * 100 ,2 ) )
,VISIBLE = 1 ;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: WIPLevel
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343818

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: DefectRatio
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The number of defects recorded in production for every million items produced
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343817

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: ProductionEfficiency
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The actual processing time as a percentage of the processing time that was estimated based on the route.
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343821

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: OntimeProductionRate
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: The percentage of production orders that were completed on or before the requested date
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS180177
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[OntimeProductionRate] AS IIF ( IsEmpty(([Measures].[ProductionOrderCount], [ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].[All])) OR IsEmpty ( ( [Measures].[ProductionOrderCount] ,[ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].&[0] ) ) AND IsEmpty ( ( [Measures].[ProductionOrderCount] ,[ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].&[0] ) ) OR ([Measures].[ProductionOrderCount], [ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].[All]) = 0 ,0 ,IIF ( IsEmpty ( ( [Measures].[ProductionOrderCount] ,[ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].&[0] ) ) ,0 ,Round ( ( [Measures].[ProductionOrderCount] ,[ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].&[0] ) / ([Measures].[ProductionOrderCount], [ProductionOrder].[DelayedProductionOrders].[All]) ,4 ) ) );
